statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT page_visited, user_id FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, ip_address FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 456 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited LIKE 'home%';
SELECT id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT page_visited, COUNT(ip_address) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_visited HAVING COUNT(ip_address) > 100;
SELECT ip_address, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited LIKE '%homepage%' GROUP BY ip_address ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, timestamp, NOW()) < 30;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY RAND() LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_table;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic_table ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic_table GROUP BY visitor_id;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_table WHERE purchase_amount > 100 ORDER BY interaction_timestamp ASC;
SELECT visitor_id, interaction_type, interaction_timestamp FROM user_behavior_table WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_table WHERE website_id = 1 ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic_table GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT visitor_id, interaction_type, purchase_amount FROM user_behavior_table WHERE purchase_amount > 1000 ORDER BY interaction_timestamp ASC;
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS page_visit_count FROM website_traffic_table GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY page_visit_count DESC;

SELECT website_id, visitor_id, interaction_type, purchase_amount FROM website_traffic_table INNER JOIN user_behavior_table ON website_traffic_table.visitor_id = user_behavior_table.visitor_id WHERE purchase_amount > 500;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 1001;
SELECT page_url, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, activity_type FROM user_behavior ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM shopping_experience WHERE user_id = 2002 ORDER BY purchase_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE page_url LIKE '%Homepage%' ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT page_visited, AVG(cart_total) AS average_cart_total FROM shopping_experience GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY average_cart_total DESC;

SELECT u.user_id, ub.activity_type, ub.page_visited, se.cart_total FROM user_behavior ub JOIN shopping_experience se ON ub.user_id = se.user_id JOIN website_traffic wt ON se.user_id = wt.visitor_id JOIN in_memory_users u ON u.id = ub.user_id WHERE ub.activity_type = 'purchase' AND se.cart_total > 100 ORDER BY se.purchase_timestamp DESC;

SELECT u.user_id, u.name AS user_name, wt.page_url, se.purchase_timestamp FROM in_memory_users u JOIN website_traffic wt ON u.id = wt.visitor_id JOIN shopping_experience se ON u.id = se.user_id ORDER BY se.purchase_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT user_id, page_id FROM website_visits WHERE visit_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_name, page_url FROM page_views ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT user_id, action FROM user_behavior WHERE behavior_time >= '2022-02-01' AND behavior_time <= '2022-02-28';
SELECT first_name, last_name, email FROM user_profiles WHERE phone_number IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM user_profiles ORDER BY first_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_visits GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 10;
SELECT page_name, page_url, visit_count FROM page_views WHERE visit_count > 100 ORDER BY visit_count DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT u.user_id, u.first_name, u.last_name, COUNT(*) AS total_actions FROM user_profiles u JOIN user_behavior b ON u.user_id = b.user_id GROUP BY u.user_id, u.first_name, u.last_name;
SELECT user_id, email FROM user_profiles WHERE phone_number IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE price < 50;
SELECT session_id, session_start, session_end FROM sessions ORDER BY session_start DESC;
SELECT page_url, time_visited FROM page_views WHERE page_id = '123456' ORDER BY time_visited ASC;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE date_registered > '2022-01-01';
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE category = 'Electronics' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT p.product_name, u.username FROM products p JOIN purchases pur ON p.product_id = pur.product_id JOIN users u ON pur.user_id = u.user_id;
